---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Dog Daycare Software" description="Dog daycare software that saves you 15+ hours per week. Online bookings, capacity management, report cards, and automated billing for daycare facilities.">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-navy to-gray-900 text-white py-16">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="badge-primary mb-4">Dog Daycare Software</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Dog Daycare Software That Saves Time & Boosts Profits</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Reduce phone calls by 60% with 24/7 online booking. Eliminate double-booking with real-time capacity management. Give staff clear schedules and daily task lists.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4">Start Free Trial</a>
          <a href="/pricing/" class="btn-secondary text-lg px-8 py-4">View Pricing</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">What Is Dog Daycare Software?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          <strong>Dog daycare software</strong> is an all-in-one system that handles reservations, deposits, packages, vaccination records, capacity, report cards, owner messaging, and billing. The best platforms also include reminders (arrivals, pickups, vaccines), digital signatures, and real-time dashboards so you know who's in-house, who's late, and what's next.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
          At PetCare.Software, we built tools specifically for mixed facilities—so if you also run <a href="/dog-boarding-software/" class="link">dog boarding</a>, a <a href="/kennel-software/" class="link">kennel</a>, or even a <a href="/cattery-software/" class="link">cattery</a>, you can manage everything from one login.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Must-Have Features</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-red flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong class="text-brand-navy">Online bookings & deposits:</strong> 24/7 reservations with optional deposits to reduce no-shows.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-red flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong class="text-brand-navy">Capacity & playgroup rules:</strong> Real-time controls to avoid overbooking—by weight class, temperament, or room.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-red flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong class="text-brand-navy">Owner portal:</strong> Clients upload vaccine proofs, sign waivers, update contact/pet info, and pay online.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-red flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong class="text-brand-navy">Report cards & media:</strong> Branded updates with notes, photos, or links to short videos.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-red flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong class="text-brand-navy">Add-ons & upsells:</strong> Offer enrichment, nail trims, baths, or late pickup fees during checkout.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Spreadsheets vs. Software</h2>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
          <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b-2 border-gray-200">
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-brand-navy">Capability</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-brand-navy">Spreadsheets</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-brand-navy">PetCare.Software</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Capacity control</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600">Manual; easy to overbook</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600">Real-time rules by playgroup</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Vaccination compliance</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600">Notes only; no alerts</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600">Expiry tracking + reminders</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Owner self-service</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600">Limited or none</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600">Full portal: bookings, payments</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Reminders</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600">Manual</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600">Automated SMS/email</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">FAQs</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Is dog daycare software hard to learn?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">No. Modern systems are built for speed at the front desk. Teams typically learn check-in/out and report cards in a single shift.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Can owners book and pay online?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Yes. Pet parents can book, pay deposits, upload vaccines, sign waivers, and view balances in the owner portal—any time, from any device.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Will it increase revenue?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Typically yes—by reducing no-shows with deposits/reminders and by offering enrichment or grooming add-ons in the booking flow.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-red to-brand-red-dark text-white">
    <div class="container-custom text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Upgrade Your Daycare?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Ditch the spreadsheets and give your team their time back. Book a demo and see how PetCare.Software handles bookings, capacity, and report cards.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn bg-white text-brand-red hover:bg-gray-100 text-lg px-8 py-4">
        Start Your Free Trial
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
